 xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614092\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614092\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kdu1665702642851.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kdu1665702642851.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kdu1665702642851.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kdu1665702642851\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Defines the base URL used to find the related resources of the HTML widget. The value can be a directory or file.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__p_d102269e1_d102270e1_d102271e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n                                BaseURL\n                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">BaseURLName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__table_d12044e1_d12045e1_d12046e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__table_d12044e1_d12045e1_d12046e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__table_d12044e1_d12045e1_d12046e1__entry__2\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kdu1665702642851__table_d12044e1_d12045e1_d12046e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">BaseURLName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kdu1665702642851__table_d12044e1_d12045e1_d12046e1__entry__2\">Absolute path of a directory or file; directory\n                     name must end in a slash, file should not. For example:\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">D:/docs/index.html</code> or\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://www.mycorpfotos.com/images/</code>\n<p class=\"p\">If not specified, the working directory is used as the default.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__section_ygf_53t_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d777589e110\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__table_d12689e1_d12690e1_d12691e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Yes </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__section_zyg_v3t_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d777589e156\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__p_d102278e1_d102279e1_d102280e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Base URL</span> is used to\n            calculate the location of relative references to other resources, such as images, in the\n            HTML content. For example, if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Base URL</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://localhost:8086/resources/</code> and the widget contains the\n            following image reference:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__pre_ov4_w3t_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;img src=\"image1.png\"&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__p_d102281e1_d102282e1_d102283e1\">…the complete image URL is\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">http://localhost:8086/resources/image.png</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__p_d102284e1_d102285e1_d102286e1\">If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Base URL</span> has no value, it\n            uses the working directory as the base URL.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__p_d102287e1_d102288e1_d102289e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Base URL</span> property works\n            in the same way as the HTML <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;base&gt;</code> tag. Thus, if you set the\n            property to <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://mywebapp/images/</code>, it has the same effect as the\n            following tag in the HTML:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__pre_sv4_w3t_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;base href=\"http://mywebapp/images/\"&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__p_d102290e1_d102291e1_d102292e1\">If the HTML content of the widget contains a\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;base&gt;</code> tag, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Base URL</span> property is\n            ignored.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__section_mtp_z3t_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d777589e214\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__p_d102296e1_d102297e1_d102298e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__pre_tmj_1jt_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"baseurl=http://localhost:8086/resources/\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdu1665702642851__section_oj4_1jt_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d777589e233\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ied1665702642247.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ied1665702642247.html\" title=\"The uhtml widget is a field-level widget in a form component that renders HTML code (including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript) or displays a web page (when the field value is a URL prefixed by an ampersand (&amp;www.mysite.com/doc/index.html). Uniface provides a logical widget called HTML, which is mapped to uhtml.\">uhtml (HTML Widget)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$properties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldproperties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614092\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614092\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Base URL (BaseURL) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Defines the base URL used to find the related resources of the HTML widget. The value can be a directory or file. \" BaseURL = BaseURLName \" Value Description BaseURLName Absolute path of a directory or file; directory name must end in a slash, file should not. For example: D:/docs/index.html or http://www.mycorpfotos.com/images/ If not specified, the working directory is used as the default. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description The Base URL is used to calculate the location of relative references to other resources, such as images, in the HTML content. For example, if Base URL is http://localhost:8086/resources/ and the widget contains the following image reference: <img src=\"image1.png\"> Copy …the complete image URL is http://localhost:8086/resources/image.png . If Base URL has no value, it uses the working directory as the base URL. The Base URL property works in the same way as the HTML <base> tag. Thus, if you set the property to http://mywebapp/images/ , it has the same effect as the following tag in the HTML: <base href=\"http://mywebapp/images/\"> Copy If the HTML content of the widget contains a <base> tag, the Base URL property is ignored. Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics. $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"baseurl=http://localhost:8086/resources/\" Copy Applies To uhtml (HTML Widget) Related Links $properties Return or set the current widget properties of a field. $fieldproperties Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}